      <title>中国共产党第三次全体会议关于改革的决议要点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/highlights-of-china-cpc-third-plenum-s-resolution-on-reforms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国周日全文公布了《关于进一步深化改革推进中国现代化的决定》，这些政策是中国共产党中央委员会上周召开的全体会议上讨论的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/highlights-of-china-cpc-third-plenum-s-resolution-on-reforms</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 11:12:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾与中国就争议海域任务达成谅解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/philippines-china-reach-understanding-on-disputed-sea-missions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾称，为缓解紧张局势，该国已与中国就其向南海军事前哨基地的补给任务达成“临时协议”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/philippines-china-reach-understanding-on-disputed-sea-missions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 11:05:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙部长对法国左翼的最低工资计划表示欢迎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/macron-minister-warms-to-the-french-left-s-minimum-wage-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国内政部长杰拉德·达尔马南表示，最低工资标准可能会提高，这为争夺下届政府政策影响力的左翼阵营的一项关键提议打开了大门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/macron-minister-warms-to-the-french-left-s-minimum-wage-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 11:05:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国将完善金融业监管机制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/china-to-improve-supervision-mechanism-for-finance-industry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据中国共产党对世界第二大经济体的长期规划，中国将完善对 66 万亿美元金融业的监管机制，规范各种金融活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/china-to-improve-supervision-mechanism-for-finance-industry</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 10:56:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列内塔尼亚胡将于周二会见正在康复的拜登</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/israel-s-netanyahu-will-meet-with-recovering-biden-on-tuesday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本杰明内塔尼亚胡的办公室表示，他将于周二在华盛顿会见美国总统乔拜登，此前一天，以色列总理将向国会联席会议发表讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/israel-s-netanyahu-will-meet-with-recovering-biden-on-tuesday</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 10:24:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰军队面临包围风险 放弃顿涅茨克村庄</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/war-in-ukraine-kyiv-s-forces-flee-donetsk-village-to-avoid-encirclement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[DeepState 地图服务在 Telegram 上表示，乌克兰军队撤出了顿涅茨克地区的普罗赫雷斯村，因为他们面临被俄罗斯军队围困的危险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/war-in-ukraine-kyiv-s-forces-flee-donetsk-village-to-avoid-encirclement</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 09:57:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平誓言重塑中国财政，帮助负债累累的地方</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/xi-vows-more-local-government-support-in-new-economic-blueprint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国执政党共产党公布了针对世界第二大经济体的长期蓝图，国家主席习近平也公布了旨在提振中国负债累累的地方政府财政的全面计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/xi-vows-more-local-government-support-in-new-economic-blueprint</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 09:13:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国面临严峻选择：公务员薪酬上涨迫在眉睫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/uk-faces-fiscal-hole-if-labour-grants-above-inflation-pay-awards</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据报道，公共部门工资上涨导致英国财政缺口高达 100 亿英镑（129 亿美元），英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 表示，如果英国不提供高于通胀率的工资增长，英国将面临再次罢工和护士和教师短缺的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/uk-faces-fiscal-hole-if-labour-grants-above-inflation-pay-awards</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 08:27:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国法院在致命冲突后取消了大部分工作配额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/bangladesh-orders-shoot-on-sight-ahead-of-job-quota-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周，在孟加拉国首都爆发学生暴力抗议活动后，该国最高法院废除了备受争议的政府就业配额制度的大部分内容。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/bangladesh-orders-shoot-on-sight-ahead-of-job-quota-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 07:54:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列袭击也门港口城市以回应胡塞无人机袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/israel-says-it-struck-targets-in-houthi-controlled-red-sea-port</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列袭击了也门胡塞武装控制的红海港口荷台达周围的目标，以报复伊朗支持的武装分子对特拉维夫的无人机袭击，这次袭击造成一名男子死亡，并暴露了以色列防空系统的弱点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/israel-says-it-struck-targets-in-houthi-controlled-red-sea-port</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 16:48:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
